The purpose of the study is to characterize the immunogenicity & safety of a booster dose of GSK Biologicals' meningococcal vaccine 134612 given at 12-15 months of age or at 15-18 months of age (co-administered with Infanrix(R)) in healthy toddlers primed with GSK Biological's Hib-meningococcal vaccine 792014.

 This study is single-blinded for the primary phase and open-label for the booster phase.

